<taxonomicName box="[688,796,1420,1446]" pageId="11" pageNumber="144">
<emphasis box="[688,796,1420,1446]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="144">obtusifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
” and “ 
<taxonomicName box="[876,998,1420,1446]" pageId="11" pageNumber="144">
<emphasis box="[876,998,1420,1446]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="144">ceratophylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
”: “Las hojas de los tallos floríferos, parecidos algo á los de la 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="11" pageNumber="144" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rosmarinifolia">
